criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  women attending obstetrics & gynecology (OB-GYN), family planning, general medicine,
             family medicine or HIV/Sexually transmitted disease (STD) clinic

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  non-English speaking other than Spanish speakers

          -  accompanied by a child >3 years of age without adequate provision for child care;

          -  Visually- or hearing-impaired women;

          -  without access to a telephone;

          -  Severe Mental impairment
